# Baked into `vite build`. Use a relative path so the browser calls the same host
# that serves the SPA (Railway monolith or local uvicorn). Avoids CORS when you
# open the built app at http://127.0.0.1:8000/ etc.
# Override at build time only if the API is on another origin (then set CORS on the API).
VITE_API_URL=/api
